            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-white/80 italic mb-4">"The workshop let me come up with my own style, which is huge especially as a brand founder."</p>
            <div>
              <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-white">Khe Hy</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/50">Founder, RadReads</p>
